WEBVTT

00:00.150 --> 00:01.851
Previously on "Devious Maids"...

00:02.593 --> 00:04.349
We have to go to the police.

00:04.350 --> 00:06.263
They need to know the truth
about Flora.

00:06.264 --> 00:08.250
Why?
They already arrested someone.

00:08.251 --> 00:09.700
Maybe he didn't do it.

00:09.701 --> 00:11.405
I wanna get out of here, mom.

00:11.406 --> 00:13.037
I'm working on it, baby.

00:13.038 --> 00:15.991
We're hoping to find someone
to live in.

00:15.992 --> 00:17.872
That's the situation
that I'm looking for.

00:17.873 --> 00:19.231
What about the girl who got killed?

00:19.232 --> 00:22.595
Those people she worked for,
they're... strange.

00:22.596 --> 00:25.944
Are you ambitious, Marisol?

00:26.539 --> 00:28.707
I found a lawyer for immigration.

00:28.708 --> 00:31.043
He said that he can help me
bring Miguel to America.

00:31.044 --> 00:34.012
Who's Miguel?
That's her kid back in Guadalajara.

00:34.013 --> 00:35.680
I like waiting on you.

00:35.681 --> 00:39.518
Rich boys? They never fall
in love with the help.

00:39.519 --> 00:41.019
Do you have a crush on me?

00:41.020 --> 00:42.687
I'm not admittin' nothing.

00:42.688 --> 00:45.490
This is Bonita's replacement?
Her name is Carmen.

00:45.491 --> 00:46.792
The only reason I took this job

00:46.793 --> 00:48.727
was so I could become friends
with Alejandro.

00:48.728 --> 00:51.029
If you play him your music,
I will fire you.

00:51.030 --> 00:53.999
What is this?
It's nothing.

00:54.000 --> 00:56.101
Carmen!

00:56.102 --> 00:57.537
Aah!

00:58.671 --> 01:01.541
Odessa! Are you okay?

01:07.502 --> 01:09.368
So when does Odessa get back
from the hospital?

01:09.369 --> 01:10.515
It should be about a week.

01:10.516 --> 01:11.983
But you don't gotta worry
about a thing.

01:11.984 --> 01:14.253
Carmen and I are gonna take
great care of this place.

01:16.255 --> 01:17.890
See that you do.

01:24.630 --> 01:26.898
So what do we do first?

01:27.590 --> 01:30.145
I say lets get crazy
and wax the floors.

01:32.004 --> 01:33.573
Carmen?

01:35.196 --> 01:36.698
It's not right.

01:36.699 --> 01:38.000
What's not?

01:38.001 --> 01:39.512
Alejandro's never here.

01:39.513 --> 01:41.607
Between his other houses
and all his touring,

01:41.608 --> 01:44.515
he's in this house, what,
ten weeks a year?

01:44.516 --> 01:46.451
If that.

01:46.452 --> 01:49.454
Most of the time,
this amazing place is empty.

01:49.455 --> 01:52.757
Nobody sits on the silk sofa.
Nobody plays the grand piano.

01:52.758 --> 01:54.604
So what?
So it's immoral.

01:54.605 --> 01:57.763
If God blesses you with nice things,
He expects you to use them.

01:57.764 --> 01:59.030
Carmen!

02:02.001 --> 02:04.135
We have to enjoy
what God has given us.

02:04.136 --> 02:05.436
This is our way to thank Him.

02:05.437 --> 02:07.138
Uh, what are you doing?

02:07.139 --> 02:09.273
Well, if Alejandro won't thank God
for His many blessings,

02:09.274 --> 02:11.377
I think someone
should do it for him.

02:13.178 --> 02:16.381
What about the waxing?

02:16.382 --> 02:17.982
Yeah, we'll get to it...

02:17.983 --> 02:20.018
after I spend 20 minutes
in this pool...

02:20.019 --> 02:21.487
thanking God.

02:25.124 --> 02:26.724
What's wrong?

02:26.725 --> 02:29.227
Nothing.

02:29.228 --> 02:31.699
I just didn't know you were this...

02:32.965 --> 02:34.699
Religious?

